54:57.720 --> 55:01.720
then you can identify 5 types of production.

55:01.720 --> 55:05.720
This is design production.

55:06.500 --> 55:10.500
The production equipment is transported to the place where the product is produced.

55:10.500 --> 55:14.500
What is the example? Construction.

55:14.500 --> 55:18.500
The next type is the production of products by order.

55:18.500 --> 55:22.500
Sometimes it is also called small-scale production.

55:22.500 --> 55:26.500
