55:47.280 --> 55:51.280
with extremely high technical characteristics.

55:51.280 --> 55:55.280
Another example is the diamond-diamond complex.

55:55.280 --> 55:59.280
Each specific limited precious stone

55:59.280 --> 56:03.280
