57:01.620 --> 57:05.620
The production is flexible.

57:05.620 --> 57:09.620
This type is characterized by high intensity

57:09.620 --> 57:13.620
and highly qualified work.

57:13.620 --> 57:17.620
It should be noted that re-orders

57:17.620 --> 57:21.620
