58:07.180 --> 58:11.180
The production of products in batches is carried out

58:11.180 --> 58:15.180
when the volume of production is required

58:15.180 --> 58:19.180
and the operation can be repeated.

58:19.180 --> 58:23.180
The distribution of production volumes is large enough

58:23.960 --> 58:27.960
