01:08:36.340 --> 01:08:40.340
It should be noted that at the current pace of production updates,

01:08:40.340 --> 01:08:44.340
it is necessary to constantly monitor the maintenance

01:08:44.340 --> 01:08:48.340
of the maximum possible proportionality of production.

01:08:48.340 --> 01:08:52.340
Because the rearmament of one unit

01:08:53.120 --> 01:08:57.120
or some kind of focus improvements in their activities

01:08:57.120 --> 01:09:01.120
