01:09:15.120 --> 01:09:19.120
In parallel with production,

01:09:19.900 --> 01:09:23.900
the main processes of production are carried out in parallel.

01:09:23.900 --> 01:09:27.900
Parallelity is realized at all levels of the organization.

01:09:27.900 --> 01:09:31.900
Parallel execution of the main processes can be realized,

01:09:31.900 --> 01:09:35.900
for example, by processing parts at the same time

01:09:35.900 --> 01:09:39.900
in the assembly-assembly work, so-called network graphics work.

01:09:39.900 --> 01:09:43.900
Parallel execution of the main and auxiliary operations

01:09:43.900 --> 01:09:47.900
can be achieved by combining the time of machine processing,

01:09:48.680 --> 01:09:52.680
the time of installation and removal of parts,

01:09:52.680 --> 01:09:56.680
