01:10:17.460 --> 01:10:21.460
the work of the factory is provided by the acceleration of the turnover of the means.

01:10:21.460 --> 01:10:25.460
At the workplace, it is achieved by reducing the time of the auxiliary,

01:10:25.460 --> 01:10:29.460
so-called interoperational breaks,

01:10:29.460 --> 01:10:33.460
during the execution of each operation.

01:10:33.460 --> 01:10:37.460
At the site and in the production workshop,

01:10:37.460 --> 01:10:41.460
it is done by transferring the semi-finished products from one workplace to another.

01:10:41.460 --> 01:10:45.460
Interoperational breaks.

01:10:46.240 --> 01:10:50.240
Under the directness of the organization of the production process,

01:10:50.240 --> 01:10:54.240
it is understood that the shortest path of the product passing through all stages of operations

01:10:54.240 --> 01:10:58.240
corresponding to the production process is provided.

01:10:58.240 --> 01:11:02.240
From the launch of the production of raw materials and raw materials,

01:11:02.240 --> 01:11:06.240
to the release of the finished product.

01:11:06.240 --> 01:11:10.240
In accordance with these requirements, for example,

01:11:10.240 --> 01:11:14.240
the mutual location of buildings and structures on the territory of the enterprise,

01:11:15.020 --> 01:11:19.020
the production process must be carried out in a short time.

01:11:19.020 --> 01:11:23.020
Material flow.

