To ensure the full use of equipment,

01:11:27.020 --> 01:11:31.020
material resources and working time,

01:11:31.020 --> 01:11:35.020
the achievement of rhythm is of great importance.

01:11:35.020 --> 01:11:39.020
The principle of rhythm is assumed by the uniform release of products

01:11:39.020 --> 01:11:43.020
and the rhythmic course of the production process.

01:11:43.800 --> 01:11:47.800
The rhythmic release of products means the production of the same amount of products

01:11:47.800 --> 01:11:51.800
in an equal period of time, the so-called monotony of production.

01:11:51.800 --> 01:11:55.800
The rhythm of production is expressed in the repetition of production processes

01:11:55.800 --> 01:11:59.800
through equal periods of time and the execution of the same amount of work

01:11:59.800 --> 01:12:03.800
