the maximum load of equipment is ensured,

01:12:28.580 --> 01:12:32.580
normal operation is improved

01:12:32.580 --> 01:12:36.580
by using material and energy resources and working time.

01:12:36.580 --> 01:12:40.580
Unrhythmic work of each section leads to a violation of the normal course of production.

01:12:41.360 --> 01:12:45.360
The very important value of determining methods of rhythm

