01:19:49.500 --> 01:19:53.500
the process strategy,

01:19:54.280 --> 01:19:58.280
which determines the choice of ways of production of goods

01:19:58.280 --> 01:20:02.280
and the justification of production capacity,

01:20:02.280 --> 01:20:06.280
the geographical strategy of the placement of new products in other regions,

01:20:06.280 --> 01:20:10.280
the production organization strategy,

01:20:10.280 --> 01:20:14.280
which determines the organizational structure of the enterprise,

01:20:14.280 --> 01:20:18.280
the choice of forms and methods of organization of work within the enterprise structure,

01:20:18.280 --> 01:20:22.280
the construction of work sites, the provision of their resources,

01:20:23.060 --> 01:20:27.060
the service strategy of production,

01:20:27.060 --> 01:20:31.060
which determines the form of organization of the technical, logistical, warehouse,

01:20:31.060 --> 01:20:35.060
transport and other services of the enterprise,

01:20:35.060 --> 01:20:39.060
the quality strategy,

01:20:39.060 --> 01:20:43.060
which is responsible for the so-called total quality management.

