01:32:13.000 --> 01:32:17.000
or cellular placement, formation of technological cells,

01:32:17.000 --> 01:32:21.000
as this method is sometimes called,

01:32:21.000 --> 01:32:25.000
involves a certain grouping of various equipment

01:32:25.000 --> 01:32:29.000
in the so-called technological cells,

01:32:29.000 --> 01:32:33.000
in which the full production of products

01:32:33.000 --> 01:32:37.000
with the same or similar methods and requirements for production is carried out.

01:32:37.780 --> 01:32:41.780
However, it should be noted that it can be used

01:32:41.780 --> 01:32:45.780
in small-scale production more effectively.

01:32:47.780 --> 01:32:51.780
Group technology also requires

01:32:51.780 --> 01:32:55.780
that technological classification is carried out for all components of the product,

01:32:55.780 --> 01:32:59.780
providing easy identification of each element,

01:32:59.780 --> 01:33:03.780
and, accordingly, a suitable encoding system is used,

01:33:04.560 --> 01:33:08.560
allowing to easily and quickly select technological cells

01:33:08.560 --> 01:33:12.560
and equipment necessary for the production of the appropriate product.

01:33:12.560 --> 01:33:16.560
Another principle of equipment placement

01:33:16.560 --> 01:33:20.560
is the principle of maintenance of a mobile object.

01:33:20.560 --> 01:33:24.560
It is implemented in those exceptional cases,

01:33:24.560 --> 01:33:28.560
when the product, due to large dimensions or mass,

01:33:28.560 --> 01:33:32.560
remains in one place during the entire production process.

01:33:33.340 --> 01:33:37.340
The most vivid example can be given as a shipbuilding ship.

01:33:37.340 --> 01:33:41.340
Some construction facilities,

01:33:41.340 --> 01:33:45.340
and even such production activities are far from the main production,

01:33:45.340 --> 01:33:49.340
as a film production process.

01:33:49.340 --> 01:33:53.340
At the same time, it should be said that many production facilities

01:33:53.340 --> 01:33:57.340
are a combination of various types of equipment placement

01:33:57.340 --> 01:34:01.340
and organization of the process.

01:34:02.120 --> 01:34:06.120
At the same time, there are quite serious computer tools

01:34:06.120 --> 01:34:10.120
