01:43:15.720 --> 01:43:19.720
and in a number of other assembly works.

01:43:19.720 --> 01:43:23.720
The biggest advantage and benefit from the placement of the process

01:43:23.720 --> 01:43:27.720
according to the principle of cell formation is produced

01:43:27.720 --> 01:43:31.720
